Cyberpunk style: A vast neon-lit control room with a massive holographic display showing interconnected glowing pathways and nodes representing data flows. A solitary figure in a sleek jacket stands before the console, orchestrating streams of luminous packets that branch into different colored channels - some gold for premium access, some silver, some free-flowing blue. Digital gates and checkpoints pulse along each pathway, filtering and directing traffic. The scene is bathed in deep purples, electric blues, and hot pinks, with rain-streaked windows revealing a sprawling futuristic cityscape beyond. Floating interface panels display abstract graphs and flowing metrics. The atmosphere conveys controlled power - the sense of managing chaos through elegant systems.
